author: The Critical Drinker
description: Join us as we take a look at he trailer for 28 Years Later: The Bone Temple, review the latest episode of Alien Earth and ask oursevles... how the hell are Amazon STILL pressing ahead with Phoebe Waller-Bridge's Tomb Raider? title: Open Bar #156 - Bone Temple, Alien Earth, Tomb Raider Happening After All?!
